{"tid":887230,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個坐巴士遇過癡線佬既經歷","createTime":"2018-11-02T17:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T17:53:20.000Z","uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"882965fbe7fc534e7bca4f125ee94096628c9d2b","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我每次搭巴士<br />\n都會有唔好既經歷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得有一次放左學搭巴士番屋企<br />\n搭搭下 有個站上左個癡線佬<br />\n佢就坐係我個行左邊個窗 <br />\n而我係另一邊個窗<br />\n佢成程就不斷大叫<br />\n叫到成車人嘈到無一個訓到教<br />\n仲係咁玩人格分裂<br />\n明明男人老狗<br />\n一時變左阿妹 一時又老母<br />\n一時又突然好似好正常咁講野<br />\n但內容都係奇奇怪怪<br />\n成車啲人都驚鬼左佢<br />\n坐佢隔離個打工仔仲嚇到成程扮訓<br />\n <br />\n不過都好彩同佢有啲距離 <br />\n叫做有兩個人隔下<br />\n不過因為我落車個個站近總站<br />\n所以坐我同佢隔離個兩個人都落左車<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁就出事啦</span><br />\n<br />\n佢突然開始望住我say hello <br />\n咁我就驚到癡左線 開始扮訓唔理佢<br />\n當聽唔到 唔理佢 望都唔望過去<br />\n屌你老母 點知佢臨落車前走黎拍我膊頭<br />\n同我講：Hello 我想問你幾多歲呀？<br />\n即刻嚇到我想走 但佢又塞住左我 走唔到<br />\n<br />\n我想問呢個情況你地會點比反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知可能長左啲 Sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"27f1cc1de351e473273f64bd6067e626ef1bb74a","tid":887230,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"講埋落去先啦，所以跟住你點做？"},{"pid":"2c5a0710ed06697bbbf45afc4ca3ba67287a4f35","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"27f1cc1de351e473273f64bd6067e626ef1bb74a","tid":887230,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"講埋落去先啦，所以跟住你點做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"最後我見巴士剩低既乘客都無人幫我<br />\n咪自己問個癡線佬咩事 （其實已經驚到傻左<br />\n點知佢又係問番我同一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就兩個一直僵持到佢落車為止<br />\n由佢落車到我落 我個口同對腳都仲震緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b427e4460750e2088c54f5e20ccb842f8c4764","tid":887230,"uid":206241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"有個老人家瘋狂大聲笑，個表情仲要好猙獰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12db457647cf0a6903c83180308a5564a2b04ab0","tid":887230,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"你有壓力我有壓力你做乜挑釁我"},{"pid":"2696eb8cce09d62fca4b47bd359b2410f94a721c","tid":887230,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d27ee4fb8ecb10218c23cbc8f2ff9d2ff0cb3db1","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"依家係香港地想正正常常坐程巴士都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係有個廢老坐隔離郁身郁世 嘈嘈閉<br />\n就係開大喇叭大大聲聽歌聽錄音既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2347fca2b6dd2a79ccf41d68c462850a50c8de0d","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2696eb8cce09d62fca4b47bd359b2410f94a721c","tid":887230,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"你係真好彩定唔搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9687b525dbcfe60f0b93a634399a4cb324735433","tid":887230,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba6d2557ca53e45b83491dd59fa9a85abd7ad1d","tid":887230,"uid":126256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"落車前啦啦叫仲未到站既我記得帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4efbf768d966276b538a40c7f7209fd2597bfd","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9687b525dbcfe60f0b93a634399a4cb324735433","tid":887230,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d27ee4fb8ecb10218c23cbc8f2ff9d2ff0cb3db1","tid":887230,"uid":215046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"依家係香港地想正正常常坐程巴士都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係有個廢老坐隔離郁身郁世 嘈嘈閉<br />\n就係開大喇叭大大聲聽歌聽錄音既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"係香港人缺少左一份公德心 同理心<br />\n淨係識理自己 但完全唔諗自己做緊既<br />\n會點樣影響或者騷擾到其他既人<br />\n未遇過係好事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c74dc7fc58efbd721d25abba6fc818989e30ff","tid":887230,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8BocDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8BocDK.jpg&h=2caa7562&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b901f3eea299689fd5de80d7784128a4c31264db","tid":887230,"uid":160093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"中學放學 <br />\n想遊巴士河 搭左架冇咩人嘅車<br />\n到中途 望到左後排有個男人怪怪地 <br />\n原來佢打緊丁<br />\n比我發現仲繼續打到拎紙巾出黎 <br />\n當年驚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}